data.description: Come make this charmer in fast-growing Fate your new home. This burgeoning community offers all the conveniences of city living, along with quaint feeling that small town Texas provides. Just mere minutes away from bustling downtown Fate, this 2017 Pulte build provides many amenities to make this house feel like home. The open floor plan, elevated ceilings, wood flooring, and oversized kitchen island create an ambiance that sticks with you. Recent upgrades include new carpet and interior paint in the common areas and master bedroom. Great location close to I-30 and TX-66 allow for quick travel to Rockwall and Dallas. Come see this one today before it's gone!
